					<TD bgColor=white class=view>&nbsp; &nbsp; <font color=#010080><a href='mailto:magu@moneytoday.co.kr'>김재승</a> 기자 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 08/29 11:11 &nbsp; | &nbsp; 조회 5571 &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></TD></TR>
